text: Roeland Pruijssers (born 16 August 1989) is a Dutch chess grandmaster. ==Chess career== Born in 1989, Pruijssers earned his international master title in 2007 and his grandmaster title in 2012.1st quarter Presidential Board 2012, 3-6 February, Al Ain, UAE FIDE He won the Leiden Open in 2016, scoring 7/9. He is the No. 16 ranked Dutch player as of February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Chess grandmasters Category:Dutch chess players Category:Sportspeople from Hendrik-Ido-Ambacht
